translate ru UnionKingdom10_f9db763d:
    # "Sarah was sitting at her desk."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_89f762ef:
    # "In front of her were a series of books on the subjects of political philosophy."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_da348d4b:
    # "Sarah had read her share, growing up in Castle Reinmeer."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_b4b05006:
    # "Still, she felt wholly unprepared for the question before her."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_170fcb12:
    # "Rosanna had always balanced the interests of the nobility and commonfolk."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_55dfe9b9:
    # "It was a balance that had worked well enough over the centuries to maintain a peace."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_c545df02:
    # "Marion's uprising had shattered that fact."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_ae6817f3:
    # "The truth was that the nobility was now weaker than it had ever been."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_86a43124:
    # "In part, Sarah appreciated that fact."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_e83e94f3:
    # "Difficult questions, long held off by the entrenched powers, were suddenly up for debate."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_294d6839:
    # "The increased social mobility of the commonfolk had motivated many to develop new industries, adding to the prosperity of her nation."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_e02d74e7:
    # "Yet..."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_66f4de04:
    # "Sarah also knew the dangers of antagonizing the nobility."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_16cc25ca:
    # "In defending her country from the Tribes, she had been too short-sighted in considering the interests of the Old Houses."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_91f85326:
    # "In turn, thousands had died in the fighting."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_655b4e96:
    # "Sarah did not want to risk such a tragedy again."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom10_779c208c:
    # "She began to consider."
    ""

